<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Typification.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
There are three sheets of the type collection of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="microsepala">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Ipomoea microsepala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
at K, of which the sheet with bar code 000612734 was annotated as holotype by McDonald. Since there seems no particular reason why this sheet was identified as the holotype in preference to the others, we are here lectotypifying it to remove any uncertainty.
</paragraph>
